arStrings.szText: "You wish to travel to Maugan's Folly?"
Truthfully, no. Maugan's Folly is a stain on the Zakarum's history and a reminder of my own mistakes. But I must return to collect my master's armor.
The memory is fresh and painful.
Without her armor, I cannot continue her name. I cannot be a crusader. Her name dies and everything she fought for dies with it.
